In the following the invention will be explained by example in conjunction with drawings, wherein:


FIG. 1 is a schematic cross sectional view of a prototypical variant of a vacuum packing configuration according to the invention;


FIG. 2 is a view similar to FIG. 1 and building on the representation of FIG. 1, of a preferred embodiment of the vacuum packing configuration;


FIG. 3 is a longitudinal section through a preferred embodiment of a vacuum treatment installation according to the invention;


FIG. 4 is a sectional view of the packing configuration according to the invention in a further embodiment;


FIGS. 5(a), 5(b), 5(c) and 5(d) are respective top plan views of possible forms of the packing configuration according to the invention;


FIG. 6 is a schematic sectional view of a driving configuration for the workpiece holding fixture on the installation according to FIG. 3;


FIG. 7 is a schematic sectional view of the driving configuration according to FIG. 6, further developed for an installation in principle according to FIG. 3, in which the workpiece holding fixtures comprise at least workpiece holders for two workpieces; and


FIG. 8 a is a sectional view of a further embodiment of a packing configuration according to the invention.
